name: She's in Portland
description: Hoping to reconnect with his college buddy, a 30-something businessman drags him along on a road trip.

review.author: MZan99
review.heading: Beautifully Shot Movie
review.reviewBody: Road trip movie after being stuck inside for months. Count me in. This movie had gorgeous cinematography. Doesn't look like it was made on an indie film budget. Tommy and Francois have a great dynamic. I want to buy that Bronco!
